You say &quot;ready&quot; and it ports you into an instanced training zone or a mini 20 minute solo quest zone or something.  You complete the zone mission (like an ldon) and you ding.  If you fail, no biggie or xp loss or anything, but maybe have to pay 1000p or something to try again.<br>
<br>
